735
00:35:52,100 --> 00:35:54,160
But there needs to be something done to make up for the stupidity.

736
00:35:54,160 --> 00:35:55,820
Something besides me saying I am sorry.

737
00:35:55,820 --> 00:35:56,820
And of course I am sorry.

738
00:35:56,820 --> 00:35:59,860
And then said, for context, I was high as a kite on pain meds.

739
00:36:00,220 --> 00:36:04,820
Never introduce meds as a way of excusing a thing you did wrong.

740
00:36:04,820 --> 00:36:06,340
It never makes anyone feel better.

741
00:36:06,340 --> 00:36:07,820
It's really tricky.

742
00:36:07,820 --> 00:36:21,680
And, like, I think there is a thing here which is part of the reason that the firestorm has not been quite as immediate and harsh as the one in response to Con Zealand was that I think a lot of people have a lot of goodwill to these two people in this area.

743
00:36:21,900 --> 00:36:30,420
But I think the problem is that if you leave it too long to apologise, that goodwill erodes and then people are like, ah, if that goodwill was justified, they would have apologised by now.

744
00:36:30,420 --> 00:36:33,120
