00:36:47,920 --> 00:36:53,860
I mean, I'm not sure Glasgow did, but, well, they kind of had to apologise for Chengdu, though, in a way.

751
00:36:53,860 --> 00:36:55,660
Well, yeah, but that wasn't their fault.

752
00:36:55,660 --> 00:36:56,860
That wasn't their fault.

753
00:36:56,860 --> 00:37:11,240
