762
00:37:45,500 --> 00:37:49,040
And these are the people who are responsible for disseminating it.

763
00:37:49,140 --> 00:37:51,420
And this is a timeline we're aiming to work to.

764
00:37:51,420 --> 00:37:54,060
And then things will just happen quickly.

765
00:37:54,060 --> 00:38:01,980
